title: The Best Paranormal News Show
cleaned_text:
First Half: Plasma physicist John Brandenburg, Ph.D. has worked in defense, energy, and space research. He'll reveal strong evidence for a thermonuclear event having happened on Mars, as well as the progress being made on a manned mission to Mars.

Second Half: After a long successful career as an attorney Michelle Welch came out as an empath and intuitive, helping others and teaching classes on crystals, tarot, energy work, and intuition. She'll discuss inspirational spirits like angels and spirit guides, scarier entities such as ghosts and demons, and how to protect yourself against psychic attacks.
